text: The Girl from Moon Bridge () is a 1953 Finnish drama movie directed by Matti Kassila and starring Tyyne Haarla, Ansa Ikonen, Paavo Jännes, Kullervo Kalske, Arvo Lehesmaa, Kaisu Leppänen, Joel Rinne, Eero Roine. ==Other websites== * Category:1953 drama movies Category:Finnish movies Category:Movies directed by Matti Kassila
title: The Girl from Moon Bridge
